---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-10">
    <h1 class="font-sans text-3xl font-medium mb-6 text-primary">About Fatawa Library</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-stone dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p>Fatawa Library is a curated archive of Islamic legal rulings (fatāwā) from major scholars, translated into English for the benefit of English‑speaking readers.</p>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>We strive to provide accurate, reliable translations of fatwas from trusted scholars, with full references to original Arabic sources. All content is reviewed for accuracy.</p>
      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>Translations are for informational purposes only. Always consult a qualified scholar for personal religious guidance.</p>
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>For corrections or inquiries, please email <a href="mailto:fatawalib@example.com" class="text-accent hover:underline">fatawalib@example.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>